dev-tools.description: Tools for the Datagrok developers (TestManager, DevPanel). [Learn more](https://github.com/datagrok-ai/public/blob/master/packages/DevTools/README.md)

sqlite.description: SQLite is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform that provides support for importing and previewing SQLite files.

tutorials.description: The package contains a collection of interactive materials helping users explore the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform.

chem.description: Cheminformatics support: import, rendering, sketching, calculation of properties, predictive models, augmentations, multiple analyses. [Learn more](https://github.com/datagrok-ai/public/blob/master/packages/Chem/README.md)

demo.description: *Demo* is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform. It demonstrates the [scripting](https://datagrok.ai/help/compute/scripting) functionality for [Python](https://www.python.org/), [R](https://www.r-project.org/), [Julia](https://julialang.org/), [NodeJS](https://nodejs.org/), [Octave](https://octave.org/).

sequence-translator.description: SequenceTranslator is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform, used to translate [oligonucleotide](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oligonucleotide) sequences between [different representations](https://github.com/datagrok-ai/public/tree/master/packages/SequenceTranslator#sequence-representations).

clinical-case.description: Provides support for dealing with clinical data represented in the [SDTM](https://www.cdisc.org/standards/foundational/sdtm) format.

pubchem-api.description: Integration with the PubChem web service.

peptides.description: Advanced tools for analyzing collections of peptides.

marvin.description: marvin is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform.

oligo-batch-calculator.description: Calculates the following oligonucleotide properties: Length, Optical Density, NMoles, Mass, Molecular Weight, Extinction Coefficient (using nearest neighbour method)

drug-bank.description: DrugBank is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform.

api-tests.description: Automated tests for the [Datagrok JS API](https://datagrok.ai/js-api)

multiplot.description: MultiPlot is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform. MultiPlot was developed in purpose to provide to user ability to easily create dashboards based on complex data which have common influencing parameter (usually presented as axis X on charts). Common axis X combined with compact form of presenting charts allow user quickly estimate data meaning.

charpy.description: ChaRPy package extends Datagrok viewers with two commands 'To Python script' and 'To R script', which translate a selected viewer to Python or R code, respectively, along with executing this code for displaying the resulting plot. The two commands are available via a hamburger menu (a top-left button in a viewer's header), and supported for most of the viewers in Datagrok.

compute.description: Provides additional analytical and UI blocks for [Datagrok scientific computing](../../help/compute/compute.md).

chembl.description: Chembl integration, commonly used queries and browser

widgets.description: A collection of commonly used widgets, viewers, filters, and cell renderers.

charts.description: Charts package provides visualizations built using the [ECharts](https://echarts.apache.org/en/index.html) library.

bio-signals.description: BioSignals is a package for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platfrom. The goal of the project is to offer an efficient and automated biosignal processing routine.

dsp.description: A pack of various digital signal processing tools

multi-form.description: MultiForm viewer provides a convenient way to visualize a set of selected rows.

chembl-api.description: Similarity and substructure search in ChEMBL using its API

custom-ml.description: CustomML is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [custom machine learning models](https://datagrok.ai/help/learn/custom-ml-models).

ketcher.description: Adds [Ketcher](https://lifescience.opensource.epam.com/ketcher/index.html) as an optional molecular sketcher.

bio.description: Bioinformatics support (import/export of sequences, conversion, visualization, analysis). [See more](https://github.com/datagrok-ai/public/blob/master/packages/Bio/README.md) for details.

sunburst.description: Sunburst chart for the datagrok platform

vdj-tools.description: VDJtools is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform.

leaflet.description: Interactive map with a number of extensions that uses Leaflet.js

sequence.description: Support for the biological sequences (DNA, RNA, proteins), including FASTA readers, 3D visualization of molecules, MSA viewer, and functions for working with sequences

file-editors.description: Support for editing end previewing multiple file formats (PDF, SVG)

power-grid.description: PowerGrid contains popular spreadsheet extensions, such as [sparklines](#sparklines) and support for [images](#images).

alation.description: Alation is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform.

arrow.description: Arrow is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform that provides us with the opportunity to work with parquet and feather file formats.

helm.description: Provides support for HELM notation (importing, detecting, rendering, conversion). [Learn more](https://github.com/datagrok-ai/public/blob/master/packages/Helm/README.md)

gis.description: GIS (geographic information system) functionality, such as maps and geocoding. [Learn more](https://github.com/datagrok-ai/public/blob/master/packages/GIS/README.md)

phylo-tree-viewer.description: *PhyloTreeViewer* is a [Datagrok package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for phylogenetic trees visualization.

chem-draw-sketcher.description: ChemDraw is a [package](https://datagrok.ai/help/develop/develop#packages) for the [Datagrok](https://datagrok.ai) platform.
